---
title: Sunday Beyond Meat® and Lentil Stew with Potatoes and Garlic Toast
description: This hearty stew tastes like it has been simmering for hours, but it's done in just 30 min! Sour cream brings a touch of creaminess to this Beyond Meat®, veggie and lentil wonder, while crispy, buttery dill-garlic toast is perfect for dipping.
